  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine almond flour and coconut oil. Mix until the mixture is crumbly.",
    "Add in heavy cream and salt. Stir gently until evenly combined.",
    "Place the crumble mixture onto a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Bake for 10-12 minutes or until golden brown and crispy on top.",
    "Serve warm as a snack."
